This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image generation and reconstruction. The use of Deep Learning and Neural Networks also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The use of Recurrent Neural Networks also suggests that it could belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category. Finally, the use of Convolutional Neural Networks suggests that it could belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
